oracle.pg.rdbms.index.oratext

Class OracleTextQueryObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.rdbms.index.oratext.OracleTextQueryObject

  • public class OracleTextQueryObject
extends Object
    This class defines a helper Query object used for querying K/V pairs indexed using an Oracle Text index.
